text: Gavray-sur-Sienne is a commune in the Manche department in north-western France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Gavray (the seat), Le Mesnil-Amand, Le Mesnil-Rogues and Sourdeval-les- Bois.Arrêté préfectoral 12 December 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Manche department ==References== Category:Communes of Manche
title: Gavray-sur-Sienne
